 "remarks": "This bright and airy two-bedroom duplex spans two levels and offers picturesque views of Main Street. Fully reimagined through a complete gut renovation, the residence seamlessly blends modern design, exceptional comfort, and top-tier energy efficiency.  The sun-filled open-concept layout features gleaming white oak floors, expansive windows, quartz countertops, and a sleek Bosch stainless steel appliance suite. Both bedrooms offer beautifully appointed ensuite, spa-inspired bathrooms, while additional highlights include a home office space, recessed lighting throughout, and a charming private porch. Ideally situated in the heart of town, this exceptional home is just moments from acclaimed restaurants, boutique shopping, the commuter express train, and the very best of in-town living.",
